  "summary": "This ERC is a new NFT asset designed based on the user contract wallet (including account abstraction), and is forward compatible with [ERC-721](./eip-721.md). To keep NFT assets simple, this ERC removes the `approve`, `setApprovalForAll`, `getApproved`, `isApprovedForAll` and `safeTransferFrom` functions of ERC-721.",
  "title": "Simple NFT, Simplified ERC-721"
